title: Silver Support / Jungle main looking for duo partner + competitive 5-man team
body:
Looking for any players wanting to duo que / casually 5-man team play during preseason and season 8 this year, aiming to climb with people willing to be competitive and tilt-proof whilst developing a good working friendship, add my IGN 'Two In The Bush.'

Cheers and see you in the rift.
